      <span class="ln"><span><span class="chrome-txt">Marketing</span></span></span>
      <span class="ln"><span><span class="chrome-txt">cast in</span></span></span>
      <span class="ln"><span><span class="oil-txt">metal.</span></span></span>
    </h1>
    <p class="sub">I'm Swapnil Biswas - a product marketer who builds. I forge the agents, sites and SEO systems behind <b>657K+ leads</b> and <b>18M+ in organic traffic</b>, not just the decks that describe them.</p>
    <div class="cta">
